msgid "desc_task_100_stage_1"
msgstr "Test your skills against the monsters of Agon and reap the rewards!"

msgid "desc_task_101_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"No normal person would accept this mission. Demon queens are half- demon, "
"half-spider, 100% deadly. Existing since the ancient era of Agon, they are "
"survivors with great adaptability. Intelligent and sinister, demon queens "
"hunt Agonians and feast on their terror. It takes a deep understanding of "
"spiders to defeat them in their domain. Killing 400 of them seems natural to "
"you, this will prove you are worthy of the title \"the Spider\"."

msgid "desc_task_102_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Long ago you committed a horrible crime, your reputation seemed to be "
"permanently tarnished. That all changed when monsters began killing innocent "
"people in your community. With no one left to turn to the others realized "
"you were their only hope. This is your opportunity to atone for your crimes, "
"all you have to do is hunt and kill the monsters known as evil eyes."

msgid "desc_task_103_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Moose hunting can be quite enjoyable, the bigger the rack, the more "
"successful the hunt."

msgid "desc_task_104_stage_1"
msgstr "Test your skills against the monsters of Agon and reap the rewards!"

msgid "desc_task_105_stage_1"
msgstr "Test your skills against the monsters of Agon and reap the rewards!"

msgid "desc_task_106_stage_1"
msgstr "Test your skills against the monsters of Agon and reap the rewards!"

msgid "desc_task_107_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"A malicious brood of brown chickens snuck into your house and soiled your "
"carpet. This was not the first time they struck but it will be the last."

msgid "desc_task_108_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"You are an expert on clothing, knowing how to dress nicely and comfortably. "
"Clothes are your passion and you enjoy making fine garments for yourself as "
"well as others. To continue your pursuit, you have decided to go on a "
"journey to collect an abundance of supplies. Collecting twenty thousand "
"cotton from her bushes is no easy task, but to you, it only feels natural. "
"Prove that you love what you do, people all across Agon will know you as the "
"Clothier."

msgid "desc_task_109_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Many people in Agon consider it a death wish to challenge a cairn giant but "
"you are no ordinary fighter, you're a veteran. It takes cunning, agility and "
"power to defeat a cairn giant, all which you possess. A dangerous task lies "
"ahead, you are to seek out their encampments and lower their population. "
"Killing 400 cairn giants could be an early trip to the grave but you are "
"fearless. Success will be a great achievement, earning you a reputation as "
"\"the Death Dancer.\""

