msgid "desc_task_117_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"There is much speculation about the origin of hooded ones. These forsaken "
"souls are damned for eternity. There are those who believe that if they gaze "
"into their undead eyes they will be capable of stealing the unholy power the "
"hooded ones possess. Those lucky enough to survive are forever twisted and "
"whether or not their quest was successful is anyone's guess."

