msgid "desc_task_124_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Courage, compassion, and loyalty are a few of your virtues. Overcoming "
"impossible odds is something you are well known for. Due to this, it was no "
"surprise to anyone when you stepped forward to challenge a particularly "
"fearsome tribe of marauding fire giants. Show them the skill you possess and "
"the sharpness of your blade."

msgid "desc_task_125_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Air, earth, fire, and water, the four elements. It is said that all "
"character traits can be traced back to one of these four, including negative "
"traits such as gluttony and hate. Overcoming the frailties of mankind can "
"only be accomplished by facing them directly. By disposing of the elements "
"themselves, you can thus shed yourself of all shortcomings, or so it has "
"been told."

