msgid "desc_task_133_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"You are a person with many dark thoughts, making  you a natural for "
"manipulating unholy energy. During dusk you are most comfortable and you "
"feel at home in the shadows. Many consider you a mastermind but that's not "
"good enough. You desire power and respect. It is within your grasp, all you "
"have to do is take it. Travel to the home of the varangians and perfect "
"necromancy by hitting them with seventy-five hundred cursed bolts. People "
"will then know you as \"The Necromancer.\""

