msgid "desc_task_159_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"When it comes to the wild jungle of Yssam, raptors are the most ruthless "
"hunters to be found. Possessing razor-sharp claws and vicious jagged teeth, "
"raptors cut their prey to bloody shreds and feast on their flesh. They are "
"breeding rapidly, expanding their domain, and as a result, are killing many "
"people by the day. This is where you come in. For the right price, you will "
"prove that you are above the most dangerous creatures in the jungle or on "
"the food chain. You will prove that you are worthy of being called The "
"Dinosaur Hunter."

msgid "desc_task_159_stage_2"
msgstr ""
"You've hunted the raptors and greatly reduced their numbers. It is now time "
"for the final test, a very dangerous one. Now you will seek out the alphas "
"of the pack, the deathstalker raptors. Take the ferocity of a raptor and "
"double it, that's how you'd best describe a deathstalker. Your hunting "
"skills will be greatly put to the test, you might not survive to tell the "
"tale. Should you succeed, no one can say anything, you are The Dinosaur "
"Hunter."

msgid "desc_task_160_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Why not use a trap, they said? It's barbaric, they said. Hey, we've all got "
"our methods, yours just happens to involve blowing up vermin, what's wrong "
"with that?"

msgid "desc_task_161_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Rabbits are a bigger problem than people think, if someone doesn't put them "
"in check their rapid breeding will get out of control.  First they'll take "
"over the city, then they'll take over the land,  then they'll take over the "
"world. Fortunately for the civilians you're here to make sure that doesn't "
"happen. Time to go rabbit hunting."

msgid "desc_task_162_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"With the power of the lightning, you strike your enemies, zapping their "
"flesh and blowing them away like the raging storm. There are many kinds of "
"magic in Agon, but none as violent or destructive as the energy you harness. "
"Thriving on chaos and destruction you sweep the lands of those who dare "
"stand in your way, stepping ever closer to unraveling the deepest secrets of "
"your craft. Storm Magi are known as wildcards among sorcerers. Very few "
"mortals hold this title and those who do are held in high regard but also "
"met with fear. To begin, slay lizardmen with your ball lightning spell."

msgid "desc_task_162_stage_2"
msgstr "Next you must slay earth elementals with your ball lightning spell."

msgid "desc_task_162_stage_3"
msgstr "Next you must slay evil eyes with your ball lightning spell."

msgid "desc_task_162_stage_4"
msgstr ""
"For your final task, slay cairn giants with your ball lightning spell. Good "
"luck."

msgid "desc_task_163_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Fire. As mesmerizing as it is wondrous, it can both create and destroy. "
"You've spent years learning to shape and control the flame, it has become "
"your plaything. Despite your incredible skill, you have room for "
"improvement. After reading through a dusty tome you found on the top shelf "
"of the mages guild you read stories of mages able to become one with the "
"flame through shamanic practices. \n"
"It was awkward at first, your dancing skill was poor and singing was a "
"talent you never possessed. Over time your skills grew and just as you began "
"to doubt the methods of shamanism you felt a spark of energy deep within, it "
"was at that moment that you realized you had found your calling."

