msgid "desc_task_169_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"In olden days the best archers of Chaldea were called Raven Gods and "
"Goddesses. This tradition spread throughout Agon and very few earned the "
"title. As the strongest breed of hobgoblins, ravens are considered to be the "
"ultimate test in bow to bow combat, a true test of archery skill. Many "
"hopeful archers sought out to prove their skill but for every one that "
"succeeded, a dozen failed. It's a brutal and deadly tradition."

msgid "desc_task_16_stage_1"
msgstr "To start your journey as a Demon slayer kill 50 Shadow Spirits."

msgid "desc_task_16_stage_2"
msgstr ""
"You now need to kill 25 Hooded Ones to complete this stage of Demon slaying."

msgid "desc_task_16_stage_3"
msgstr ""
"Next kill 20 Shadow Knights to move onto the final stage of Demon slaying."

msgid "desc_task_16_stage_4"
msgstr ""
"End the life of 5 Demon to complete your task of Demon slaying and reap your "
"final rewards."

