msgid "desc_task_173_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Cats are known to fear and respect the alpha, it's just a matter of time "
"before you establish who that is..."

msgid "desc_task_174_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Spying, theft, assassination, you can do it all. Whether under the veil of "
"night or the light of day, you are the right person for the job. You play "
"dangerous games and have the will and guts to attempt the seemingly "
"impossible, which is about to come in handy yet again. Are you ready to "
"prove yourself?"

msgid "desc_task_175_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"There is no better game to hunt than deer. Not only are their pelts valuable "
"but their meat is delicious."

msgid "desc_task_176_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"The moons of Agon are known as Leen and Neith. Leen is the red moon and once "
"per year, it becomes blood red. During this day hundreds of monsters known "
"as knights are born. The blood moon blades are tasked with the quest of the "
"eradication of the blood knights. Your initiation into the order is to fight "
"for their cause and prove your worth."

msgid "desc_task_177_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"Merchant ships work hard to find the safest routes across the sea. They know "
"how to avoid the krakens...most of the time, but pirates are smarter and "
"more unpredictable. One legendary crew known as the Darkblade Buccaneers has "
"proven to be among the scariest sights to encounter. Mercilessly plundering "
"on both land and sea, these pirates are both wealthy and menacing. They only "
"select the most elite pirates to join their ranks and to prove your worth "
"you must slaughter many, many bonecrew, their sworn enemies. Only then may "
"you join their ranks."

msgid "desc_task_178_stage_1"
msgstr ""
"In Agon, many people have referred to shadow knights as warriors of "
"darkness. They are sinister, wicked and chaotic, truly beings of evil. Known "
"for assassination, thievery, spying, and sabotage, their motives are for an "
"unholy cause. The people need a warrior who can stand up to them, you are "
"the hero who can. You are a person of honor, glory and kindness, a warrior "
"of light. Prove to the people you are their champion, they will forever know "
"you as The White Knight."

